                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                    Single-Page Design
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Eliminated multi-step friction with integrated payment flow
                    and smart form design
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center">
